            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-92456bb7-f146-490a-9153-5f479443d78c">
                The Prime Minister (Sir Winston Churchill)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-92456bb7-f146-490a-9153-5f479443d78c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
